          <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">$297<span class="text-sm">/month</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm mb-4">$1,000 Setup</div>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>• AI Growth Strategy Session</li>
            <li>• Plug & Play AI Website</li>
            <li>• Lead-Capturing AI Chatbot</li>
